{
  "title": "Flaky Herbal Kenyan Pasta Pilaf",
  "description": "A delicious and diabetic-friendly Kenyan dish featuring flaky texture and a hint of herbal flavors. This easy-to-make pilaf is perfect for a quick weeknight dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
